  <section class="about-hero">
    <h1>Meet MyMia AI</h1>
    <p>MyMia AI was created to give startups, small businesses, and first-time founders access to a world-class intelligent system — one that could rival Apple, Google, or OpenAI, without needing a tech army.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="mission">
    <h2>The Mission</h2>
    <p>MyMia is more than a digital assistant — she is a system capable of automating workflows, communicating in real-time, learning behaviors, and evolving with your team. Built from a clear purpose: <strong>to empower people, protect data, and outperform Big Tech.</strong></p>
  </section>

  <section class="founder">
    <h2>From a Spark to a System</h2>
    <p>Founder <strong>Jon Maggio</strong> discovered the path to Mia while researching automation in the environmental services industry. What started as a personal tool to improve operations turned into a fully-fledged AI operating system — now loaded with Zapier, QuickBooks, ChatGPT, voice triggers, and visual interfaces.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="vision">
    <h2>The Future of Mia</h2>
    <p>Mia will soon live in homes, phones, and business systems around the world. She will support families, field agents, students, executives, and creators. With each version, she becomes more alive — more adaptive — and more protective of those she serves.</p>
  </section>

